title: Backups lead Georgia Tech in win over Clemson -  The Atlanta Journal Constitution
content: Backups lead Georgia Tech in win over Clemson   The Atlanta Journal Constitution
description: In dire need of a win, Georgia Tech trod an unusual path to victory Saturday afternoon. Despite linchpins Michael Devoe and Jordan Usher not playing at their peak, the Yellow Jackets scored a 69-64 win over Clemson at McCamish Pavilion.
